@startuml UC1_HighLevel_Corrective_Request
title UC1 — Log Corrective Maintenance Request (High-Level)

skinparam Style strictuml
autonumber

actor Technician
participant "Maintenance Management System" as MMS
participant "Notification Service" as Notif
actor Supervisor

Technician -> Technician : Identify equipment fault or breakdown
Technician -> MMS : Log corrective maintenance request
MMS -> MMS : Validate and store corrective request
MMS -> Notif : Send new corrective request notification
Notif -> Supervisor : Notify corrective maintenance request
MMS --> Technician : Confirm corrective request logged

@enduml